        "districts": [
            "A space station contains two caps and a cylinder that ",
            "rotates to create comfortable gravity.  The cylinder ",
            "contains a rectangular grid of districts.  The left and ",
            "right edges may contain port districts.  The top and ",
            "bottom wrap around.  Each district is optimized for ",
            "some types of buildings but is less effective for ",
            "others.  Each district can contain up to four large ",
            "buildings (100x100), sixteen medium buildings (50x50) ",
            "or sixty-four small buildings (25x25)."]},
